<p>Implementing ERP Systems requires more than a good understanding of the system software, it also requires detailed knowledge of the entire field of manufacturing. Our team is well versed in Manufacturing Basics and trains not only with Infor but with APICS as well. We know ERP. We also know manufacturing. <em><strong>This ensures you get an implementation partner who can successfully support your project.</strong></em></p>
